rk experience opportunities for two candidates from this programme each year commitment to climate action we are committed to operating our business in an environmentally responsible and sustainable manner platinum continues its longstanding commitment to combating climate change with the measurement and offsetting of its carbon footprint  “funds under management fum” ie the amount of money that we manage is the key variable for platinum’s business model and an important determinant of our profit  fum is significantly influenced by performance of our individual funds and investment mandates  click on the “funds under management” tab on our shareholder information page to see the history of fum  click here to see the latest fum data for each of the funds managed by platinum  australian institute of company directors spasx boards  february   equal opportunity for women in the workplace agency “eowa” australian census of women in leadership  women executive key management personnel  workplace gender equality agency “wgea” gender workplace statistics at a glance february   eowa australian census of women in leadership   wgea gender workplace statistics at a glance february   australia bureau of statistics “abs” cat  labour force australia march   abs cat  migrants education and work australia may   abs cat  education and work australia may   abs cat  australian aboriginal and torres strait islander health survey   the  annual scholarships are spread over the university of canberra griffith university curtin university latrobe university and deakin university platinum investment management ltd company profile  bloomberg feedback platinum investment management ltd private company company profile sector financials industry asset management subindustry investment management platinum investment management limited operates as an investment management firm the company specializes in investing in international equities platinum investment management serves clients worldwide cor